page.title: 04MY HOME-LEONIE TOWNSEND
page.content: My home was built in{1886}and is a {semi-detached}house.My home is part of the{Tetcott Housing Estate}.Tetcott is a very small village set in the {countryside},and is three miles away from the nearest school which is {Clawton.C.P.school. }The village of Tetcott has got one{post office}and {General Stores}and no other shops. The house that I live in is rented by{'The Hunt'}.My father is the huntsman and kennel Huntsman of the {South Tetcott Hunt}.In his job he has to pick up dead animals,he then has to bring them back to the kennels to skin them and the next day he feeds it to the{hounds. I have lived in my house for two years.The{view}from the front upstairs room's window is lovely.You can see for{miles.
